        "title": "fix(channel): harden local setup trust",
        "body": "## Summary\n- thread normalized `plugins.load.paths` into channel trusted-catalog lookup/listing so `channels add` and setup discovery can see config-path channel plugins\n- make trusted channel fallback origin-aware so untrusted `config`/`workspace`/`global` shadows fall back by `origin + pluginId` instead of suppressing safe copies globally\n- reapply the non-bundled trust gate before scoped setup-only channel imports so untrusted local channel plugins are not imported during setup unless explicitly trusted\n\n## Verification\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/channels/plugins/catalog.test.ts src/commands/channel-setup/trusted-catalog.test.ts src/plugins/channel-catalog-registry.test.ts src/plugins/loader.test.ts`\n- `pnpm build`\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local`\n",
